- `app:popUpToInclusive="true"` - This ensures that the login fragment itself is also removed from the back stack

With these changes, when navigating from the login fragment to the onboarding fragment:
1. The login fragment will be completely removed from the back stack
2. The user won't be able to press the back button to return to the login fragment
3. The back button will either exit the app or go to the previous screen before the login fragment

This ensures a one-way navigation flow from login to onboarding, which is typically what you want in an authentication/onboarding flow."}]}

