 ): LeetCodeRepository {
 return LeetCodeRepositoryImpl(remoteDataSource, localDataSource)
 }
}
```

This setup provides a complete cache management solution for the LeetCode API data based on the JSON response provided. The repository will:

1. Check for cached data first
2. Fetch from network if cache is expired or not available
3. Save successful network responses to the cache
4. Fall back to cache when network requests fail
5. Provide options to force refresh or clear the cache

The cache expiration is set to 2 hours but can be adjusted as needed."},{"role":"user","content":"<additional_data>
