 defaultConfig {
 applicationId "com.devrachit.ken"
 }

 buildTypes {
 debug {
 applicationIdSuffix ".debug"
 }
 }
}
```

This would create two separate app installations - the regular app and the debug version.

## How to Fix:

1. Open your AndroidManifest.xml
2. Look for all activities with the `LAUNCHER` intent filter
3. Keep only one activity with this filter (your main entry point)
4. Remove the LAUNCHER category from all other activities
5. If needed, use navigation components to navigate between activities

